title: The application of the wrong voting 4646.746238 GOF token
body:
Dear Golff finance community, we sent 4646.746238 GOF to the contract address by error in the voting of GOF mine pool.
I hope the team can issue additional GOF and return it to the original address.

Txid： https://etherscan.io/tx/0x8664225b77df6a57282641ccd0988c919907fa37337998eaa4c75d28bed01d1b

Num of GOF: 4646.746238

I hope to help you find the lost token. Thank you.

Jubi labs team
